                <Bold>Alpha testers</Bold>: <Image gif:ImageBehavior.AnimatedSource="/Images/cider.gif" Width="50" Height="18" Margin="0 0 0 -4" />, Flix88, <Span Foreground="#f00">kurosaki ichigo</Span>
